WEBVTT

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:40.110
[Born to Be Alive]

00:01:40.140 --> 00:01:43.160
[Episode 33]

00:01:43.210 --> 00:01:44.310
The worst case back then

00:01:44.310 --> 00:01:45.539
was County Mayor Duojie.

00:01:45.539 --> 00:01:47.200
You know about that too?

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:48.570
Yes.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:49.950
When his condition was at its worst,

00:01:49.950 --> 00:01:51.950
he came to our hospital for an X-ray.

00:01:51.979 --> 00:01:53.509
I was the attending doctor.

00:01:54.289 --> 00:01:55.620
I remember it clearly.

00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:57.360
The X-ray back then showed

00:01:57.430 --> 00:01:59.039
he had bone spur formations.

00:02:01.260 --> 00:02:01.810
So,

00:02:02.250 --> 00:02:03.440
can the medical records and X-rays

00:02:03.440 --> 00:02:04.740
still be found?

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.410
They should still be

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:11.280
in the County Hospital archives.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:12.180
But it's been so many years.

00:02:12.180 --> 00:02:13.500
I'm not sure if they're still there.

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:14.900
I'll check for you later.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:15.430
Okay.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:21.970
I've been busy lately

00:02:21.970 --> 00:02:23.060
and can't look after you.

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:23.820
Grandma has a bad back,

00:02:23.820 --> 00:02:25.579
so she can't pick you up from school.

00:02:25.579 --> 00:02:26.250
After school,

00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:27.410
go to Grandma's house by yourself.

00:02:27.410 --> 00:02:27.930
Okay.

00:02:28.670 --> 00:02:31.000
Your dad will take you to school tomorrow.

00:02:33.010 --> 00:02:35.030
You haven't been fighting lately,
have you?

00:02:35.030 --> 00:02:36.370
Who fights anymore?

00:02:37.030 --> 00:02:37.960
I get along so well

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:38.970
with Sun Luowen now.

00:02:38.970 --> 00:02:40.100
We're best friends.

00:02:41.340 --> 00:02:43.470
Who is Sun Yiwen?

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:45.130
The one who pulled my pigtails.

00:02:45.130 --> 00:02:46.300
I've told you so many times.

00:02:46.300 --> 00:02:47.430
You never remember.

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:00.190
Erzi's Mom!

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:01.970
Bring the big wooden basin

00:03:02.000 --> 00:03:03.500
over to me.

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:04.690
My goodness.

00:03:04.710 --> 00:03:06.340
I really caught this wave.

00:03:08.130 --> 00:03:09.440
The Provincial Commission and Provincial Government

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.840
have always prioritized

00:03:10.970 --> 00:03:12.400
ecological protection,

00:03:12.830 --> 00:03:13.490
especially

00:03:13.580 --> 00:03:15.510
since the 18th National Congress.

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:17.240
The wooden basin was placed in the yard,

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.250
and filled with water.

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:19.300
and pour the fish down.

00:03:19.300 --> 00:03:20.370
The meeting proposed

00:03:20.370 --> 00:03:22.020
that prioritizing ecological protection

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:23.840
must be implemented in all aspects.

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:25.000
When development

00:03:25.020 --> 00:03:26.450
conflicts with protection,

00:03:26.450 --> 00:03:28.420
we must never sacrifice the ecology

00:03:28.420 --> 00:03:29.860
and environment

00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:31.520
for temporary economic growth.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.780
Don't move. Sit still.

00:03:33.020 --> 00:03:34.950
Regarding increasing protection

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:36.820
for the Bolamula Nature Reserve,

00:03:37.079 --> 00:03:39.340
and comprehensively rectifying
and regulating

00:03:39.340 --> 00:03:41.740
the development order
of the Tianduo Coal Field,

00:03:41.740 --> 00:03:43.950
a series of measures were proposed.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:50.640
In response
to national environmental policies,

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:51.920
the provincial committee and the provincial government

00:03:51.920 --> 00:03:53.650
[Qinghai Provincial People's Government]

00:03:53.650 --> 00:03:55.710
to impose a comprehensive mining ban

00:03:55.780 --> 00:03:57.970
on all coal mines
in the Tianduo Coalfield.

00:03:57.970 --> 00:03:59.910
The billions in mining rights involved

00:03:59.910 --> 00:04:01.640
will be completely withdrawn.

00:04:02.220 --> 00:04:03.010
This is not just

00:04:03.010 --> 00:04:05.010
an ordinary administrative order.

00:04:05.090 --> 00:04:07.370
It is a self-revolution

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:10.160
in Qinghai's environmental history.

00:04:10.590 --> 00:04:12.500
It is an ecological responsibility
Qinghai shoulders

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.770
for the nation and all of humanity.

00:04:16.230 --> 00:04:18.089
When the mining pits fall silent,

00:04:18.760 --> 00:04:21.290
and the slag heaps are covered
by green grass,

00:04:22.060 --> 00:04:23.390
I suddenly understood.

00:04:23.900 --> 00:04:25.660
The Bolamula

00:04:25.690 --> 00:04:27.220
that I've been dreaming of.

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:30.180
Those days and nights
of patrolling the mountains.

00:04:30.180 --> 00:04:31.320
They turned out to be just the prologue

00:04:31.320 --> 00:04:33.200
to this ecological awakening.

00:04:33.930 --> 00:04:34.930
And today,

00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:36.700
our efforts

00:04:37.159 --> 00:04:39.300
will finally find their answer

00:04:40.220 --> 00:04:42.150
in the surging of the Three Rivers.

00:04:44.620 --> 00:04:46.600
The provincial committee and provincial government

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:47.830
have approved

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:49.520
the Implementation Plan

00:04:49.770 --> 00:04:50.840
for the Comprehensive Rectification

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:52.300
of the Tianduo Coal Field.

00:04:52.350 --> 00:04:53.220
[Secretary of Municipal Council of Zhongqu, Li Jianjun]

00:04:53.220 --> 00:04:54.620
Effective immediately,

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:56.659
mining operations in all zones

00:04:57.130 --> 00:04:58.450
of the Tianduo Coal Field

00:04:58.450 --> 00:04:59.450
must stop at once.

00:05:00.420 --> 00:05:01.430
All enterprises

00:05:01.870 --> 00:05:04.500
must complete the aftermath work
as soon as possible

00:05:04.500 --> 00:05:05.900
and withdraw gradually.

00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:08.720
Relevant departments will organize forces

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.600
to carry out cinder cleanup,

00:05:10.650 --> 00:05:11.710
slope management,

00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:13.270
pit backfilling,

00:05:13.750 --> 00:05:15.210
and grassland regreening

00:05:15.300 --> 00:05:16.600
in all mining areas.

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:23.010
After the coal mine closed,

00:05:23.930 --> 00:05:25.430
the capital income

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:27.520
will definitely be reduced.

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:29.190
The impact is multifaceted,

00:05:29.570 --> 00:05:30.950
But environmental protection

00:05:30.950 --> 00:05:32.240
is the trend.

00:05:32.770 --> 00:05:34.000
I hope everyone

00:05:34.740 --> 00:05:36.390
does not pit economic development

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:38.450
against environmental protection.

00:05:38.540 --> 00:05:39.980
We must deeply recognize

00:05:40.030 --> 00:05:42.490
the ecological status of Qinghai Province.

00:05:42.750 --> 00:05:44.470
Prioritizing ecological protection

00:05:44.470 --> 00:05:45.409
is a vital spirit

00:05:45.540 --> 00:05:46.720
that must be resolutely implemented

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:48.250
from the state

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:49.670
down to the local level.

00:05:50.100 --> 00:05:51.120
Everyone

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.930
must take a responsible attitude

00:05:52.930 --> 00:05:54.060
toward the country,

00:05:54.330 --> 00:05:55.330
the people,

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.690
and future generations

00:05:57.220 --> 00:05:58.950
to complete the important task

00:05:58.950 --> 00:06:00.680
of environmental protection.

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:02.260
Comrade Lin Peisheng.

00:06:09.140 --> 00:06:09.840
Comrades.

00:06:11.130 --> 00:06:12.360
The city currently

00:06:12.740 --> 00:06:13.950
has five coal mines.

00:06:14.830 --> 00:06:16.000
Distributed among them are

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.450
19 slag hills

00:06:17.930 --> 00:06:18.800
and 11 mining pits

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.480
of varying depths.

00:06:22.190 --> 00:06:25.080
Considering that carrying out
ecological restoration projects

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:26.880
in high-altitude mining areas

00:06:27.330 --> 00:06:28.510
is a national first,

00:06:29.570 --> 00:06:30.740
and there is no successful experience

00:06:30.740 --> 00:06:31.540
to draw upon,

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:34.450
regarding how to improve the soil,

00:06:34.620 --> 00:06:36.420
what grass varieties to choose,

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:38.250
and what the survival rate will be,

00:06:38.250 --> 00:06:39.040
we all have to

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.380
feel our way forward.

00:06:40.850 --> 00:06:42.510
We have formed an expert group

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:43.800
to work with us

00:06:43.950 --> 00:06:45.480
to draw up a treatment plan.

00:06:45.570 --> 00:06:46.310
In addition,

00:06:47.330 --> 00:06:49.480
after much consideration and discussion,

00:06:49.480 --> 00:06:50.360
we believe

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.430
we can select

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:52.820
one or two enterprises

00:06:52.930 --> 00:06:54.110
to take charge of the regreening.

00:06:54.110 --> 00:06:55.540
The enterprises must have advantages
in capital,

00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:56.310
technology,

00:06:56.400 --> 00:06:57.960
and personnel.

00:06:58.940 --> 00:07:00.900
We can better coordinate

00:07:00.930 --> 00:07:02.190
all aspects of the work

00:07:03.070 --> 00:07:06.070
to ensure the regreening project
proceeds smoothly.

00:07:07.150 --> 00:07:07.880
Manager Bai.

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:12.330
A comprehensive mining ban.

00:07:12.330 --> 00:07:13.220
So we’re shutting it down completely?

00:07:13.220 --> 00:07:14.420
Is that what you mean?

00:07:14.620 --> 00:07:16.150
That's exactly what it means.

00:07:16.150 --> 00:07:17.950
The policy has been handed down.

00:07:18.250 --> 00:07:19.580
There are no other possibilities.

00:07:19.580 --> 00:07:20.700
Shutting down completely?

00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:21.750
So everyone's unemployed now?

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:22.660
As for my old employees,

00:07:22.660 --> 00:07:23.960
I won't even mention them.

00:07:23.960 --> 00:07:25.310
But the mine just hired

00:07:25.330 --> 00:07:26.870
a dozen professionals this year.

00:07:26.870 --> 00:07:28.640
All the postgraduates and undergraduates

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.730
have to go back?

00:07:29.970 --> 00:07:31.750
Is Tianduo City going to shut down?

00:07:31.750 --> 00:07:33.480
The sky is falling.

00:07:33.500 --> 00:07:36.130
Do you think this is just
corporate downsizing?

00:07:36.130 --> 00:07:37.480
It's useless complaining to me here.

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:39.230
This is the general trend.

00:07:40.320 --> 00:07:42.250
Forget about old or new employees.

00:07:42.409 --> 00:07:43.200
Right now, whether the entire Xinhai

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:43.810
can survive

00:07:43.810 --> 00:07:45.010
is the real question.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.520
Go back to the salt field.

00:08:12.390 --> 00:08:13.190
Forget it.

00:08:15.180 --> 00:08:16.140
Don't become a target,

00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:17.140
nor block the way.

00:08:17.750 --> 00:08:19.350
Wait until the storm passes.

00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:20.270
Especially regarding those

00:08:20.270 --> 00:08:21.420
small mine owners.

00:08:21.580 --> 00:08:23.120
Pay them what's owed as soon as possible

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.220
and appease them.

00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:26.810
Don't let anyone get a handle on you.

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:28.500
The city's current policy

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:30.230
is to have a smooth transition.

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:30.860
And your Xinhai

00:08:30.860 --> 00:08:32.110
is the key focus.

00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:33.390
Director Huang,

00:08:33.909 --> 00:08:35.510
how much I've done over the years,

00:08:35.510 --> 00:08:36.890
you know the truth.

00:08:37.049 --> 00:08:38.120
You're really acting like

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:38.909
you use people when you need them

00:08:38.909 --> 00:08:40.620
and discard them when you don't.

00:08:40.620 --> 00:08:41.820
Key focus, huh?

00:08:42.169 --> 00:08:42.770
Fine.

00:08:43.260 --> 00:08:44.470
Should I invite the comrades
from the Discipline Inspection Commission

00:08:44.470 --> 00:08:45.930
to come check my books too?

00:08:46.550 --> 00:08:46.970
Feng Keqing!

00:08:46.970 --> 00:08:49.390
You're just looking for someone to blame,
aren't you?

00:08:49.390 --> 00:08:50.070
The mining ban

00:08:50.070 --> 00:08:51.600
is an order
from the provincial government.

00:08:51.600 --> 00:08:52.000
How can you expect

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:52.790
a low-ranking division-level official

00:08:52.790 --> 00:08:53.480
to stop it?

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:54.760
I don't care if it's from the province

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:55.520
or anywhere.

00:08:55.650 --> 00:08:57.180
Anyway, Xinhai can't stop.

00:08:59.860 --> 00:09:01.240
Let me tell you something.

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:02.700
During the meeting today,

00:09:03.060 --> 00:09:03.870
Lin Peisheng brought up

00:09:03.870 --> 00:09:05.270
the regreening project.

00:09:05.390 --> 00:09:06.860
If this thing is done well,

00:09:06.980 --> 00:09:08.640
everyone can benefit from it.

00:09:09.100 --> 00:09:10.320
What do you mean?

00:09:10.410 --> 00:09:11.170
Regreening?

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:13.470
What can you earn from planting grass?

00:09:13.470 --> 00:09:14.780
You want me to plant cows?

00:09:14.780 --> 00:09:15.850
What's the rush?

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:20.240
Are you stupid

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:22.040
after digging coal these years?

00:09:22.620 --> 00:09:23.290
Who told you

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.790
environmental protection is charity?

00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:26.410
Environmental protection
is an engineering project.

00:09:26.410 --> 00:09:27.670
Do you understand now?

00:09:28.140 --> 00:09:30.070
It's so exhausting talking to you.

00:09:34.890 --> 00:09:35.580
Zhuling.

00:09:36.670 --> 00:09:38.000
Stop doing. Time to eat.

00:09:38.020 --> 00:09:38.620
Come here.

00:09:40.070 --> 00:09:40.860
Stop, stop.

00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:43.150
Dad, actually, I'm not very hungry.

00:09:43.960 --> 00:09:45.400
You're not fat.
You don't need to lose weight.

00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:46.130
Stop doing your homework.

00:09:46.130 --> 00:09:47.170
No.

00:09:47.550 --> 00:09:48.350
After school,

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:49.000
Sun Luowen and I

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.190
went to get roasted buns.

00:09:50.190 --> 00:09:51.070
His treat.

00:09:52.250 --> 00:09:53.490
Then you don't have to eat.

00:09:53.490 --> 00:09:54.290
Don't have it.

00:09:54.640 --> 00:09:56.740
You'll get indigestion if you eat more.

00:09:56.740 --> 00:09:57.160
Here.

00:09:57.700 --> 00:09:58.200
Look.

00:09:58.300 --> 00:10:00.030
I kept something up his sleeve.

00:10:02.870 --> 00:10:03.600
Is it good?

00:10:04.010 --> 00:10:04.750
It's good.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:06.880
I didn't use sugar.

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:07.680
I added honey.

00:10:08.100 --> 00:10:09.030
You're amazing.

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:09.620
Right?

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:10.550
I think so too.

00:10:11.530 --> 00:10:11.960
This smoothie,

00:10:11.960 --> 00:10:13.270
it's my first time making it.

00:10:13.270 --> 00:10:13.820
Can you taste

00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:15.030
what's in it?

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:16.010
No.

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:16.550
I was talking about

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:17.800
Sun Luowen and I.

00:10:18.560 --> 00:10:19.080
I realized that

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.050
if I talk to him nicely,

00:10:20.050 --> 00:10:21.190
he understands.

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:21.740
There's no need

00:10:21.740 --> 00:10:23.800
to get physical over a disagreement.

00:10:24.050 --> 00:10:24.740
Right. You can't.

00:10:24.740 --> 00:10:26.200
Dad, add some honey for me.

00:10:26.530 --> 00:10:26.900
Let me tell you.

00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:27.840
Your personality

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:29.040
takes after your mom.

00:10:29.460 --> 00:10:31.260
Too impatient. Like a hedgehog.

00:10:31.510 --> 00:10:31.960
But sometimes,

00:10:31.960 --> 00:10:33.360
when people interact...

00:10:36.030 --> 00:10:37.490
Actually, relationships

00:10:37.500 --> 00:10:39.010
can't be rushed.

00:10:39.390 --> 00:10:40.720
You have to take it slow.

00:10:41.370 --> 00:10:42.480
Look at me, a while ago

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:43.980
work wasn't going well for me.

00:10:43.980 --> 00:10:44.780
I was anxious.

00:10:45.100 --> 00:10:45.620
But later,

00:10:45.620 --> 00:10:46.150
once the environmental policy

00:10:46.150 --> 00:10:47.150
was implemented,

00:10:47.550 --> 00:10:48.810
everything got better.

00:10:48.810 --> 00:10:49.310
Right?

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:52.200
What's wrong?

00:10:53.220 --> 00:10:53.860
Zhuling.

00:10:56.530 --> 00:10:57.440
What did you

00:10:57.620 --> 00:10:58.350
put in there?

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:04.720
How is she?

00:11:06.810 --> 00:11:07.340
It's

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:08.720
acute urticaria.

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:10.740
What did you give her?

00:11:10.740 --> 00:11:12.070
We gave her

00:11:12.250 --> 00:11:13.180
Dexamethasone.

00:11:14.270 --> 00:11:15.070
Fortunately,

00:11:15.110 --> 00:11:16.110
I didn't put much mango

00:11:16.110 --> 00:11:17.040
in the smoothie.

00:11:17.340 --> 00:11:18.410
If she had gone into anaphylactic shock,

00:11:18.410 --> 00:11:19.940
it would have been serious.

00:11:24.140 --> 00:11:26.440
When Zhuling
just started elementary school,

00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:27.250
Bai Shao sent a box

00:11:27.250 --> 00:11:28.510
of mangoes from Guangzhou.

00:11:28.510 --> 00:11:30.450
She had an allergic reaction
after eating them

00:11:30.450 --> 00:11:31.430
and was hospitalized for a week.

00:11:31.430 --> 00:11:32.290
Did you forget?

00:11:33.010 --> 00:11:33.890
Did you forget?

00:11:36.850 --> 00:11:37.540
Sorry.

00:11:38.370 --> 00:11:38.970
I'm sorry.

00:11:48.050 --> 00:11:48.780
Shao Yunfei.

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:52.430
I misspoke earlier.

00:11:53.190 --> 00:11:54.140
I know

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:56.850
you are a competent reporter.

00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:58.460
But you really aren't

00:11:58.460 --> 00:11:59.590
a competent father.

00:12:03.020 --> 00:12:03.670
But in life,

00:12:03.670 --> 00:12:05.200
you can't have it both ways.

00:12:06.470 --> 00:12:07.740
You should go back.

