He didn't face justice.

00:27:53.280 --> 00:27:54.940
Seventeen years have passed.

00:27:56.550 --> 00:27:57.180
This matter

00:27:57.180 --> 00:27:58.640
finally has a conclusion.

00:28:00.100 --> 00:28:01.690
Our old leader in Mazhi,

00:28:01.840 --> 00:28:02.770
Secretary Chen,

00:28:03.920 --> 00:28:04.520
calls me

00:28:04.550 --> 00:28:05.700
every now and then.

00:28:06.000 --> 00:28:07.590
He says once the case is closed,

00:28:07.590 --> 00:28:08.950
he'll apply to have Duojie

00:28:08.950 --> 00:28:10.560
recognized as a martyr.

00:28:18.850 --> 00:28:19.580
Understood.

00:28:24.230 --> 00:28:25.430
I have to chip in, too.

00:28:26.680 --> 00:28:28.140
Let's get this 15,000 one.

00:28:29.170 --> 00:28:29.880
I'll keep a close eye

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:30.880
on the task force.

00:28:31.160 --> 00:28:33.030
I'll make them get results
as soon as possible.

00:28:33.030 --> 00:28:33.530
Okay.

00:28:35.850 --> 00:28:36.720
Near the hospital, Wu Jiang

00:28:36.720 --> 00:28:37.740
stole a car.

00:28:37.830 --> 00:28:39.110
Surveillance shows that

00:28:39.110 --> 00:28:40.610
ten minutes before the accident,

00:28:40.610 --> 00:28:41.440
his car stopped here

00:28:41.440 --> 00:28:42.330
for 3 minutes.

00:28:42.960 --> 00:28:44.690
Then he walked into Jiege Lane.

00:28:44.700 --> 00:28:45.480
When he came out,

00:28:45.480 --> 00:28:46.040
he was holding

00:28:46.040 --> 00:28:47.070
a black travel bag,

00:28:47.070 --> 00:28:48.200
and then drove away.

00:28:49.270 --> 00:28:50.500
Can we get fingerprints?

00:28:50.500 --> 00:28:52.030
No complete fingerprints.

00:28:52.210 --> 00:28:53.290
The fabric of the travel bag

00:28:53.290 --> 00:28:54.110
is too rough.

00:28:56.170 --> 00:28:57.970
Who gave him this bag?

00:28:58.660 --> 00:28:59.070
Does this lane

00:28:59.070 --> 00:28:59.980
have any other exits?

00:28:59.980 --> 00:29:01.310
There is one other exit.

00:29:01.940 --> 00:29:03.200
But the surveillance cameras there
were broken,

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:04.260
and are under maintenance,

00:29:04.260 --> 00:29:06.120
so they didn't capture anything.

00:29:09.310 --> 00:29:10.040
Captain Bai.

00:29:10.590 --> 00:29:11.420
Could it be that Wu Jiang

00:29:11.420 --> 00:29:12.780
planned to run away long ago

00:29:12.780 --> 00:29:14.640
and hid the money here in advance?

00:29:16.110 --> 00:29:16.980
Unlikely.

00:29:18.510 --> 00:29:19.220
Wu Jiang doesn't seem like

00:29:19.220 --> 00:29:20.680
someone that meticulous.

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:22.550
If he were that calculating,

00:29:22.550 --> 00:29:23.140
he wouldn't act so flashy

00:29:23.140 --> 00:29:24.180
usually.

00:29:25.420 --> 00:29:26.050
Besides,

00:29:26.750 --> 00:29:27.480
he couldn't confirm

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:28.200
when he would

00:29:28.200 --> 00:29:29.130
be interrogated

00:29:29.460 --> 00:29:30.010
or when

00:29:30.030 --> 00:29:31.830
he would have a chance to escape.

00:29:32.070 --> 00:29:32.770
So,

00:29:33.270 --> 00:29:34.200
this must have been

00:29:34.200 --> 00:29:35.580
a spur-of-the-moment action that night.

00:29:35.580 --> 00:29:36.990
You mean

00:29:37.160 --> 00:29:38.960
someone gave it to him in person?

00:29:39.900 --> 00:29:40.880
Who could it be?

00:29:43.500 --> 00:29:44.680
Our next step is to investigate

00:29:44.680 --> 00:29:46.140
Wu Jiang's social circle.

00:29:46.460 --> 00:29:47.920
Check what they were doing

00:29:48.050 --> 00:29:49.380
at the time of the crime.

00:29:50.420 --> 00:29:50.790
This person

00:29:50.790 --> 00:29:51.810
could contact Wu Jiang on short notice

00:29:51.810 --> 00:29:52.880
and possesses some

00:29:53.310 --> 00:29:54.070
counter-reconnaissance

00:29:54.070 --> 00:29:55.110
awareness.

00:29:56.010 --> 00:29:57.380
Let's investigate in this direction first.

00:29:57.380 --> 00:29:58.090
Okay, got it.

00:29:58.090 --> 00:29:59.510
Bai, it's meeting time.

00:29:59.610 --> 00:30:00.550
I need to interrogate
the hit-and-run driver later.

00:30:00.550 --> 00:30:01.880
Tell him to postpone it.

00:30:03.180 --> 00:30:04.180
It's not Captain Xie calling the meeting.

00:30:04.180 --> 00:30:04.750
It's the Chief

00:30:04.750 --> 00:30:06.410
calling a task force meeting.

00:30:06.880 --> 00:30:07.550
What for?

00:30:07.580 --> 00:30:07.690
The current

00:30:07.690 --> 00:30:08.160
[Missing Person]

00:30:08.160 --> 00:30:09.730
forensic report shows that

00:30:09.920 --> 00:30:11.220
the body's age,

00:30:11.240 --> 00:30:13.290
height, and other physical features

00:30:13.290 --> 00:30:14.350
match County Mayor Duojie's

00:30:14.350 --> 00:30:15.350
almost perfectly.

00:30:15.350 --> 00:30:16.700
What about the clothes
found near the body?

00:30:16.700 --> 00:30:17.830
Mostly rotted away.

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:19.480
Only a few buttons remain,

00:30:19.510 --> 00:30:20.500
which are a basic match

00:30:20.500 --> 00:30:21.530
to the button of clothes

00:30:21.530 --> 00:30:23.170
County Mayor Duojie wore when alive.

00:30:23.170 --> 00:30:24.680
Then it's highly probable

00:30:24.880 --> 00:30:25.660
that the remains

00:30:25.660 --> 00:30:27.390
belong to County Mayor Duojie.

00:30:28.070 --> 00:30:28.700
Xia Jie, based on

00:30:28.700 --> 00:30:29.900
the new X-ray I found,

00:30:29.930 --> 00:30:31.330
has raised an objection.

00:30:31.530 --> 00:30:32.530
The lack of bone spur on the bones

00:30:32.530 --> 00:30:34.130
is a major suspicious point.

00:30:34.270 --> 00:30:35.480
Xia Jie only proved that

00:30:35.480 --> 00:30:36.610
the bone spur doesn't match Duojie's

00:30:36.610 --> 00:30:37.610
medical records.

00:30:37.920 --> 00:30:38.710
But these remains

00:30:38.710 --> 00:30:39.830
were already highly

00:30:39.830 --> 00:30:40.770
skeletonized.

00:30:41.400 --> 00:30:43.070
In burial cases like this,

00:30:43.180 --> 00:30:43.920
hyperplastic tissue

00:30:43.920 --> 00:30:45.270
is easily eroded.

00:30:45.480 --> 00:30:46.330
But we can't ignore

00:30:46.330 --> 00:30:48.130
the newly discovered evidence.

00:30:48.280 --> 00:30:48.950
Bai Ju.

00:30:49.440 --> 00:30:50.610
You are using 1% of

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:51.210
uncertainty

00:30:51.210 --> 00:30:52.670
to question 99% of

00:30:52.700 --> 00:30:54.480
the complete chain of evidence.

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:55.070
Chief,

00:30:55.750 --> 00:30:56.550
isn't investigating that 1%

00:30:56.550 --> 00:30:57.350
exactly what

00:30:57.380 --> 00:30:58.530
we do?

00:30:58.820 --> 00:30:59.950
With that 1% of

00:30:59.980 --> 00:31:00.460
uncertainty,

00:31:00.460 --> 00:31:01.140
who can guarantee

00:31:01.140 --> 00:31:01.980
that the conclusion drawn

00:31:01.980 --> 00:31:03.650
is 100% the truth?

00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:11.160
From Wu Jiang's car,

00:31:11.160 --> 00:31:12.400
a gun was suddenly found.

00:31:12.400 --> 00:31:13.350
The origin of this gun

00:31:13.350 --> 00:31:14.310
is inconclusive.

00:31:14.310 --> 00:31:15.140
It's suspicious.

00:31:15.140 --> 00:31:16.250
He self-harmed to undergo surgery

00:31:16.250 --> 00:31:17.750
and still knew the escape route.

00:31:17.750 --> 00:31:18.480
It's suspicious.

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:19.180
After he escaped,

00:31:19.180 --> 00:31:20.210
from whom did he

00:31:20.230 --> 00:31:21.400
get a large sum of cash,

00:31:21.400 --> 00:31:23.070
before suddenly being killed by a car?

00:31:23.070 --> 00:31:24.070
It's suspicious.

00:31:24.270 --> 00:31:25.460
These doubts make me suspect

00:31:25.460 --> 00:31:26.610
that someone is plotting

00:31:26.610 --> 00:31:27.350
to cover up

00:31:27.380 --> 00:31:29.340
the truth about Duojie's disappearance.

00:31:29.340 --> 00:31:30.470
This further proves

00:31:30.470 --> 00:31:31.890
we should be cautious in determining

00:31:31.890 --> 00:31:33.490
the identity of the remains.

00:31:36.460 --> 00:31:38.650
No one is being careless.

00:31:40.660 --> 00:31:41.090
The Ministry of Public Security

00:31:41.090 --> 00:31:42.070
Identification Center instructor

00:31:42.070 --> 00:31:43.000
told us during training

00:31:43.000 --> 00:31:43.550
that

00:31:44.070 --> 00:31:44.960
apart from DNA,

00:31:45.310 --> 00:31:46.420
all identification techniques

00:31:46.420 --> 00:31:47.400
can only disprove,

00:31:47.400 --> 00:31:48.400
they cannot serve as

00:31:48.400 --> 00:31:49.980
the sole basis for confirmation.

00:31:49.980 --> 00:31:50.610
But since Duojie

00:31:50.610 --> 00:31:51.920
has no immediate family DNA

00:31:51.920 --> 00:31:53.120
to provide evidence,

00:31:53.360 --> 00:31:54.340
biologically speaking,

00:31:54.340 --> 00:31:55.630
100% certainty

00:31:55.660 --> 00:31:57.250
can never be obtained.

00:31:57.730 --> 00:31:58.590
So what do we do?

00:32:00.810 --> 00:32:01.330
Ignoring 99%

00:32:01.330 --> 00:32:02.910
of the evidence is gone at the scene?

00:32:02.910 --> 00:32:03.370
Right?

00:32:03.720 --> 00:32:05.030
Just keep dragging this out?

00:32:05.030 --> 00:32:06.660
Drag it out until we retire?

00:32:07.340 --> 00:32:08.630
How do we answer to

00:32:08.660 --> 00:32:09.450
the family?

00:32:09.700 --> 00:32:10.920
How do we answer to the people

00:32:10.920 --> 00:32:12.220
of Tianduo and Mazhi?

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:13.610
Bai Ju.

00:32:14.110 --> 00:32:15.920
Duojie wasn't just your Captain.

00:32:15.920 --> 00:32:17.450
He was my leader too.

00:32:21.790 --> 00:32:22.770
Think about it.

00:32:29.010 --> 00:32:30.140
Meeting adjourned.

00:32:37.660 --> 00:32:39.590
Let's go. Interrogate the driver.

00:32:46.860 --> 00:32:49.120
I'm giving you a chance to come clean now.

00:32:49.510 --> 00:32:50.880
Who put you up to this?

00:32:52.600 --> 00:32:54.000
I've said it many times.

00:32:54.420 --> 00:32:55.460
It was brake failure.

00:32:55.460 --> 00:32:56.220
Lies.

00:32:58.050 --> 00:32:58.640
The traffic police

00:32:58.640 --> 00:32:59.900
accident report shows

00:33:00.150 --> 00:33:00.850
the brake system

00:33:00.850 --> 00:33:01.950
was sabotaged.

00:33:03.810 --> 00:33:04.810
Wednesday at 4 PM,

00:33:05.270 --> 00:33:06.220
the repair shop surveillance caught

00:33:06.220 --> 00:33:07.500
you working under the car.

00:33:07.500 --> 00:33:08.500
The footage is very clear.

00:33:08.500 --> 00:33:09.090
Do you need me to

00:33:09.090 --> 00:33:10.090
pull it up for you?

00:33:11.120 --> 00:33:13.040
You were deliberately sabotaging
the brakes.

00:33:13.040 --> 00:33:13.780
Weren't you?

00:33:14.400 --> 00:33:15.830
That was routine maintenance.

00:33:15.830 --> 00:33:16.560
You can check

00:33:16.590 --> 00:33:17.440
the work orders.

00:33:17.440 --> 00:33:18.300
Why would I

00:33:18.330 --> 00:33:19.270
sabotage my own brakes?

00:33:19.270 --> 00:33:20.200
To kill Wu Jiang.

00:33:20.200 --> 00:33:21.070
To stage a car accident

00:33:21.070 --> 00:33:22.160
and silence him.

00:33:22.970 --> 00:33:23.860
Let me tell you,

00:33:24.310 --> 00:33:26.170
your boss has already confessed.

00:33:26.430 --> 00:33:27.780
He ordered you to do it.

00:33:28.270 --> 00:33:29.070
Now I'm giving you a chance

00:33:29.070 --> 00:33:30.330
to speak for yourself.

00:33:31.530 --> 00:33:32.270
I... What?

00:33:32.380 --> 00:33:33.400
What silencing?

00:33:33.850 --> 00:33:34.980
I don't understand.

00:33:40.840 --> 00:33:41.930
Think carefully.

00:33:42.480 --> 00:33:43.500
If you confess honestly,

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:44.920
you're just an accomplice.

00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:46.250
You won't be in for long.

00:33:46.720 --> 00:33:48.530
But if you refuse to cooperate,

00:33:48.980 --> 00:33:49.520
we will

00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:50.890
inform the court

00:33:50.920 --> 00:33:52.440
and ask for a heavy sentence.

00:33:52.440 --> 00:33:53.460
You might never see

00:33:53.460 --> 00:33:54.460
your child again.

00:33:54.610 --> 00:33:55.010
No...

00:33:55.740 --> 00:33:56.660
Officer,

00:33:57.240 --> 00:33:58.900
what do you want me to confess?

00:33:59.440 --> 00:34:01.390
I just didn't brake in time.

00:34:01.410 --> 00:34:02.260
I am guilty.

00:34:02.290 --> 00:34:04.690
It's not too late
to change your statement.

00:34:04.900 --> 00:34:05.530
Tell me.

00:34:07.260 --> 00:34:08.280
Is there a criminal gang

00:34:08.280 --> 00:34:09.280
threatening you?

00:34:10.290 --> 00:34:12.000
Threatening your family?

00:34:13.070 --> 00:34:14.030
Criminal gang?

00:34:14.489 --> 00:34:15.219
Tell me!

00:34:15.530 --> 00:34:16.150
Bai Ju!

00:34:16.630 --> 00:34:17.340
Stop.

00:34:17.360 --> 00:34:17.880
Speak!

00:34:18.420 --> 00:34:19.030
Who is it?

00:34:19.050 --> 00:34:19.679
Come out!

00:34:21.110 --> 00:34:22.440
He was about to confess.

00:34:27.010 --> 00:34:28.929
[Chief's Office]

00:34:28.929 --> 00:34:30.110
Surveillance shows

00:34:30.300 --> 00:34:31.190
that Wu Jiang's trunk

00:34:31.190 --> 00:34:32.520
might have been opened.

00:34:32.780 --> 00:34:33.530
But this person,

00:34:33.530 --> 00:34:34.880
he avoided the cameras.

00:34:35.050 --> 00:34:36.050
While Wu Jiang was running,

00:34:36.050 --> 00:34:36.630
he received

00:34:36.630 --> 00:34:37.780
a large sum of cash.

00:34:37.810 --> 00:34:38.460
The person who handed it over

00:34:38.460 --> 00:34:39.610
also avoided surveillance.

00:34:39.610 --> 00:34:41.690
They have
strong counter-reconnaissance skills.

00:34:41.690 --> 00:34:42.360
I suspect

00:34:42.800 --> 00:34:44.340
the person who planted the gun
on Wu Jiang,

00:34:44.340 --> 00:34:45.310
then gave him money,

00:34:45.310 --> 00:34:46.400
and ordered the truck driver

00:34:46.400 --> 00:34:46.940
to kill him,

00:34:46.940 --> 00:34:48.400
is likely the same person.

00:34:48.760 --> 00:34:49.670
The most direct lead we have now

00:34:49.670 --> 00:34:50.940
is right in front of us.

00:34:51.150 --> 00:34:51.630
It's that

00:34:51.630 --> 00:34:52.900
truck driver.

00:34:53.420 --> 00:34:54.280
So I want to find a breakthrough

00:34:54.280 --> 00:34:55.010
as soon as possible

00:34:55.010 --> 00:34:56.870
to dig out the person behind this.

00:34:57.260 --> 00:34:58.130
You asked me to investigate

00:34:58.130 --> 00:34:58.920
Wu Jiang's death.

00:34:58.920 --> 00:35:00.260
That's what I'm doing.

00:35:00.730 --> 00:35:02.430
I'm sure you've realized too.

00:35:03.050 --> 00:35:03.750
There's one

00:35:03.780 --> 00:35:04.690
obvious truth.

00:35:04.820 --> 00:35:05.900
That person didn't want

00:35:05.900 --> 00:35:06.880
Wu Jiang to talk.

00:35:07.000 --> 00:35:07.920
He wanted Wu Jiang

00:35:07.920 --> 00:35:09.580
to take the truth to his grave.

00:35:11.530 --> 00:35:12.110
Okay.

00:35:14.010 --> 00:35:15.070
High suspicion,

00:35:15.900 --> 00:35:16.960
bold assumptions.

00:35:17.800 --> 00:35:19.930
But you don't have a shred of evidence.

00:35:22.170 --> 00:35:24.090
Do you think the Procuratorate will accept

00:35:24.090 --> 00:35:25.890
confessions obtained this way?

00:35:26.000 --> 00:35:26.500
Do I need to remind you
of the regulations set

00:35:26.500 --> 00:35:27.340
by the Supreme People's Procuratorate

00:35:27.340 --> 00:35:29.400
and the Ministry of Public Security?

00:35:30.010 --> 00:35:30.820
Threats,

00:35:31.280 --> 00:35:33.210
inducement, coaching, and deception.

00:35:33.210 --> 00:35:34.450
You almost ticked all the boxes

00:35:34.450 --> 00:35:35.910
in less than five minutes.

00:35:36.320 --> 00:35:36.800
Bai Ju,

00:35:37.120 --> 00:35:38.980
what exactly are you trying to do?

00:35:42.520 --> 00:35:43.390
Five minutes.

00:35:47.020 --> 00:35:47.980
But do you know,

00:35:51.940 --> 00:35:53.600
for these short five minutes,

00:35:54.630 --> 00:35:56.110
I've waited 17 years.

00:35:58.370 --> 00:35:59.570
Seventeen years ago,

00:36:00.790 --> 00:36:02.090
those people used the same kind
of car accident

00:36:02.090 --> 00:36:02.900
to target me.

00:36:04.050 --> 00:36:05.450
I survived by sheer luck.

00:36:06.750 --> 00:36:08.150
But little Zhang Yang...

00:36:10.870 --> 00:36:11.710
Back then,

00:36:13.050 --> 00:36:14.260
as a young police officer,

00:36:14.260 --> 00:36:15.590
I wasn't mature enough.

00:36:16.210 --> 00:36:17.250
Our criminal investigation methods

00:36:17.250 --> 00:36:18.100
were also very limited.

00:36:18.100 --> 00:36:19.960
There were no surveillance cameras.

00:36:19.960 --> 00:36:20.690
So in the end,

00:36:20.960 --> 00:36:22.440
it could only be classified and handled

00:36:22.440 --> 00:36:24.300
as an ordinary traffic accident.

00:36:25.600 --> 00:36:26.990
After Li Yongqiang was shot dead

00:36:26.990 --> 00:36:28.280
at the Qima'er Gold Mine,

00:36:28.280 --> 00:36:29.320
the truth of that incident

00:36:29.320 --> 00:36:30.760
was buried forever.

00:36:31.690 --> 00:36:32.820
Zhang Yang's death,

00:36:34.490 --> 00:36:36.890
the real culprit
behind the gold mine case,

00:36:38.190 --> 00:36:40.320
and Captain Duojie's disappearance.

00:36:46.280 --> 00:36:46.990
Chief,

00:36:51.170 --> 00:36:51.730
all these years,

00:36:51.730 --> 00:36:54.060
I haven't had a single good night's sleep.

00:36:54.710 --> 00:36:55.400
I'm afraid that

00:36:55.400 --> 00:36:56.460
I'll dream of them.

00:36:59.460 --> 00:37:01.020
I can't face them.

00:37:05.100 --> 00:37:05.910
Zhang Yang,

00:37:07.110 --> 00:37:07.930
He Qingyuan,

00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:10.450
and Captain Duojie.

00:37:11.870 --> 00:37:12.770
The truth of the past

00:37:12.770 --> 00:37:13.730
and the present

00:37:15.160 --> 00:37:15.880
shouldn't be hastily buried

00:37:15.880 --> 00:37:17.670
without clarity.

00:37:23.460 --> 00:37:24.110
Chief,

00:37:25.370 --> 00:37:26.640
as a police officer,

00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:27.710
I admit

00:37:27.730 --> 00:37:28.990
I lost my cool just now.

00:37:30.370 --> 00:37:31.830
But please understand me.

00:37:33.650 --> 00:37:35.510
Please give me a little more time.

00:37:36.760 --> 00:37:38.300
I just need a little time.

00:37:52.030 --> 00:37:52.780
Bai Ju,

00:37:55.940 --> 00:37:58.200
we've worked together for so many years.

00:37:58.910 --> 00:38:00.040
You have always been

00:38:00.300 --> 00:38:01.050
a trustworthy

00:38:01.050 --> 00:38:02.840
comrade.

00:38:04.690 --> 00:38:05.760
For many issues,

00:38:06.400 --> 00:38:08.000
you reflect on them yourself

00:38:08.740 --> 00:38:11.070
without needing correction from others.

00:38:11.480 --> 00:38:12.100
So now,

00:38:12.130 --> 00:38:13.380
just as you said,

00:38:15.380 --> 00:38:16.680
you are no longer calm.

00:38:19.000 --> 00:38:20.500
I'll tell Xie Yang

00:38:21.640 --> 00:38:23.700
to let you go back and rest for a while.

00:38:28.720 --> 00:38:29.430
Chief,

00:38:33.150 --> 00:38:34.170
do you mean

00:38:36.730 --> 00:38:38.390
for me to leave the task force?

00:38:39.900 --> 00:38:41.500
As a police officer,

00:38:41.940 --> 00:38:43.300
you must never let emotions control you

00:38:43.300 --> 00:38:44.990
at any time.

00:38:46.300 --> 00:38:47.830
I think if Duojie were here,

00:38:49.890 --> 00:38:51.210
he would say the same.

00:39:31.120 --> 00:39:34.830
♪ Where the forest grows lush and dense ♪

00:39:34.860 --> 00:39:39.840
♪ Rhododendrons sing
across the snowy plateau ♪

00:39:40.190 --> 00:39:46.270
♪ When your song begins ♪

00:39:46.300 --> 00:39:52.410
♪ Spring quietly arrives ♪

00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:57.410
♪ Though you are
but a creature of the wild ♪

00:39:57.590 --> 00:40:02.110
♪ Your voice sounds like music
from the heavens ♪

00:40:02.840 --> 00:40:05.010
♪ Flying in from afar ♪

00:40:05.120 --> 00:40:06.000
I haven't seen

00:40:06.030 --> 00:40:07.760
this kind of wine in a long time.

00:40:08.650 --> 00:40:09.970
Does it still taste the same?

00:40:09.970 --> 00:40:10.550
Try it.

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:26.460
Still tastes awful.

00:40:30.030 --> 00:40:30.440
Here.

00:40:41.260 --> 00:40:42.190
It's delicious.

00:40:43.920 --> 00:40:45.260
It's still sizzling.

00:40:46.740 --> 00:40:47.540
Smells great.

00:40:56.410 --> 00:40:57.540
You guys eat, too.

00:40:58.510 --> 00:41:00.240
Does watching me make you full?

00:41:02.480 --> 00:41:03.090
Bai.

00:41:04.990 --> 00:41:07.250
I heard things aren't going well at work.

00:41:07.980 --> 00:41:09.260
We know you have rules.

00:41:10.360 --> 00:41:12.420
We're not asking you to say anything.

00:41:15.810 --> 00:41:17.920
If you're unhappy, just come eat meat.

00:41:17.920 --> 00:41:18.780
We have plenty.

00:41:22.620 --> 00:41:24.020
Then I'll come every day.

00:41:25.750 --> 00:41:26.850
I'm on leave now.

00:41:27.210 --> 00:41:28.410
I have plenty of time.

00:41:32.860 --> 00:41:33.610
About Captain's case,

00:41:33.610 --> 00:41:35.270
it hasn't been cleared up yet.

00:41:36.090 --> 00:41:36.670
I...

00:41:43.000 --> 00:41:43.730
In the future, I might not even

00:41:43.730 --> 00:41:45.660
be able to wear the police uniform.

00:41:59.970 --> 00:42:01.320
If I really take off my police uniform,

00:42:01.320 --> 00:42:03.420
you think I'd want your security uniform?

00:42:03.420 --> 00:42:04.130
Put this on.

00:42:05.190 --> 00:42:05.790
It's cold.

00:42:11.970 --> 00:42:12.610
Shao.

00:42:12.980 --> 00:42:13.640
Stop there.

00:42:21.860 --> 00:42:22.910
You invited him?

00:42:23.880 --> 00:42:25.740
He came to me to drown his sorrows.

00:42:25.960 --> 00:42:27.490
He cried even more than Han.

00:42:29.080 --> 00:42:30.880
Said you don't love him anymore.

00:42:31.560 --> 00:42:32.510
You reminded me.

00:42:32.970 --> 00:42:33.790
I remember now.

00:42:33.790 --> 00:42:35.330
Go get your...

00:42:35.660 --> 00:42:37.190
that highland barley wine.

00:42:37.450 --> 00:42:38.450
-Hurry up.
-Okay.

00:42:40.850 --> 00:42:41.850
The meat is ready.

00:42:50.420 --> 00:42:51.490
Smells so good.

00:43:02.090 --> 00:43:03.490
Why are you looking at me?

00:43:05.380 --> 00:43:06.880
You look really good in that outfit.